Repodiff
========
Repodiff is python library and utility to check sanity of repository 
metadata and comparation of two repositories.

Example usage:
==============

Sanity check
------------
python repo_diff.py --verbose test_repos/different_xml_and_sql/
python repo_diff.py test_repos/sane_repo
etc...

Comparation
-----------
python repo_diff.py --compare test_repos/sane_repo test_repos/sane_repo_2/
etc...

